Users must be at least **13 years of age**. Any user found to be under 13 will be removed immediately for legal compliance.

### **2.2 Adult-Minor Interaction (ZERO TOLERANCE)**
Any member aged 18+ found to be soliciting private contact, images, or inappropriate conversation with a minor (under 18) will be **permanently blacklisted** and reported to the **Australian Centre to Counter Child Exploitation (ACCCE)** and the **NCMEC**.

### **2.3 Personally Identifiable Information (PII)**
